{"word":"H833 - אָשַׁר - ʼâshar - aw-shar' - Bless","slug":"H833","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">אָשַׁר</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Transliteration: </strong>ʼâshar"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Phonetic: </strong>aw-shar'"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Short Definition: </strong>Bless"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b>&#x05D0;&#x05E9;&#x05C1;&#x05E8;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&#x05D0;&#x05E9;&#x05C1;&#x05E8; - 'a&#x0302;shar  'a&#x0302;she&#x0302;r</b> - <i>aw-shar', aw-share'</i><p/>A primitive root; to <i>be straight</i> (used in the widest sense, especially to <i>be level</i>, <i>right</i>, <i>happy</i>); figuratively to <i>go forward</i>, <i>be honest</i>, <i>prosper: - </i>(call, be) bless (-ed, happy), go, guide, lead, relieve."},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>Cognate:</strong> <a href=\"#/H835\">H835</a>, <a href=\"#/H836\">H836</a>, <a href=\"#/H837\">H837</a>, <a href=\"#/H838\">H838</a>, <a href=\"#/H839\">H839</a>, <a href=\"#/H8391\">H8391</a>, <a href=\"#/H842\">H842</a>, <a href=\"#/H843\">H843</a>"}]}